\begin_layout Definition
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(X,d\right)$
\end_inset

 be a metric space, 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in X$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta>0$
\end_inset

.
 Then define the 
\emph on
open ball
\emph default
