\emph on
ball
\emph default
 of radius 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

 around 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 as 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
B\left(x,\delta\right)=\left\{ y\in X\colon d\left(x,y\right)<\delta\right\} .
\]

\end_inset

Similarly 
\emph on
closed ball
\emph default

\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C\left(x,\delta\right)=\left\{ y\in X\colon d\left(x,y\right)\leq\delta\right\} .
